sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor U as User
participant FE as Frontend
participant AIM as taskpilot-ai
participant C as taskpilot-contracts
participant PA as ProjectModuleAdapter
participant UA as UserModuleAdapter
participant PS as Projects module
participant US as Users module

U->>FE: Ask AI about project/user context
FE->>AIM: Send AI request
AIM->>C: Call Project/User ports
par Load project context
  C->>PA: ProjectInsightsPort or MemberAnalyticsPort
  PA->>PS: Check membership and load project data
  PS-->>PA: DTO project, task, sprint, workload
  PA-->>C: Project context DTO
and Load user context
  C->>UA: UserProfilePort or UserSkillPort
  UA->>US: Load user profile and skills
  US-->>UA: User and skill DTO
  UA-->>C: User context DTO
end
C-->>AIM: Controlled context
AIM-->>FE: AI response or pending action proposal
FE-->>U: Display result
